      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7784_p4">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Sir,</p>
      </div>
    </front>
    <body>
            <div>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7784_p5">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>At a recent interview with
        <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>M.</abbr>
                        <expan>Mister (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> <persName type="person" key="Gerwig Robert">Gerwig</persName> at <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName>, I was told
        <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>by that <persName type="person" key="Gerwig Robert">gentleman</persName> that I must
        <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>apply to you for information 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>as to the conditions under
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>which you wish our offer to be
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>submitted for the Completion
        <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>of the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gothard</placeName> works. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7784_p6">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>Up to the present time,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>we are ignorant as to the
        <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>caution money you require.
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>The mode in which payment 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>will be made, both for
        <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>work done &amp; plant put
        <pb n="2"/>
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>on the ground, and many other
        <lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>points, which it is essential
        <lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>we should know. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7784_p7">
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>I shall be obliged if you will
        <lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>give me the fullest &amp; earliest
        <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>information in order that no
        <lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>delay may arise from our
        <lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>having to communicate further
        <lb xml:id="p2-l9"/>upon these points.</p>
      <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7784_p8">
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l10"/>I am.</p>
    </div>
        </body>
    <back>
